### Key Components

#### Backend (Python)

- **`api.py`**: `VnstockAPIClient` - Xá»­ lÃ½ authentication, package listing, downloads
- **`installer.py`**: `VnstockInstaller` - Quáº£n lÃ½ quÃ¡ trÃ¬nh cÃ i Ä‘áº·t packages
- **`ui.py`**: Eel-based backend vá»›i `@eel.expose` functions
- **`config.py`**: Centralized configuration management

#### Frontend (Web)

- **HTML/CSS**: Modern, responsive UI vá»›i Vnstock branding
- **JavaScript**: Asynchronous communication vá»›i Python backend qua Eel
- **Progressive Enhancement**: Graceful degradation cho browsers cÅ©

